## When do I need this commercial license?

iolinki-master is dual-licensed. You may always use it **free of charge under the GPLv3**
(see the LICENSE file) — including in production — **provided you comply with the
GPLv3**, i.e. any work you distribute that incorporates iolinki-master is also licensed
under the GPLv3 (source available).

A **commercial license is required only if you distribute a closed-source or
otherwise proprietary product** that incorporates iolinki-master and therefore cannot
meet the GPLv3 copyleft obligations. It grants the same code under proprietary
terms, with no copyleft requirement.

