## Frequently Asked Questions

**Q: What happens after the 1-year update period?**
A: You retain perpetual rights to use the version you licensed. Extended support contracts available at 20% of original license fee per year.

**Q: Can I use iolinki-master in open-source projects?**
A: Yes — free of charge under the GPLv3, including in production, as long as your
project complies with the GPLv3 (source available under a GPLv3-compatible license).
A commercial license is only needed for closed-source / proprietary products.

**Q: Do you offer volume discounts?**
A: Yes, for Enterprise licenses or multiple Team licenses. Contact us for details.

**Q: What payment methods do you accept?**
A: SEPA bank transfer, wire transfer, and invoicing (Net 30 for established companies).

